name: SpermaXxmas
description:
Pan”: “all”, “Sperma”: “seed of life". Panspermia as theory that life exists throughout the universe. Either life particles dusts were carried by meteorites, comets, or our spaceships, the unstoppable force of life are always permeating into unthinkable places even the entirety of universe.

This is speical little seed of life baring special mission as Xmas gift. Happy holidays!❤️🎄😊
